<h2>Our commitment</h2>
<p>
  We work to keep this site accessible and easy to use. If you experience any difficulty using any part of the site,
  please contact us and we will work with you to provide the information or service you need.
</p>

<h2>Feedback</h2>
<p>
  Email us at <a href="mailto:accessibility@example.com">accessibility@example.com</a> with a description of the issue,
  the page URL, and (if possible) what device/browser you were using.
</p>

<p class="muted">Replace the email address with your real accessibility contact.</p>
